column5: Well damn  Its with great sadness I have to say Pointed and I will not be making the annual FIREWATER tour to Lakair this year do to circumstances beyond our control it wont be happening. I will look for a report and we will be there in spirit.  Biteme  So as far as I can tell the Crayola Cup is safe this year....for now!!!!!!
Thats too bad.. Ill miss ya....

Seeing as your not gonna be there Pete, maybe someone will be interested in renting your Jumbla for the Invitational  I'll also be missing the g2g this year, but will be heading up to Lakair the following week for 7 days.
